data.description: Welcome to your new investment opportunity in the heart of East Hillside Duluth! This charming tri-plex is the perfect canvas for your real estate dreams, offering not just one but three potential income streams. It's time to unlock the incredible potential of this property and start your rental journey today!  Situated in a prime location, this tri-plex boasts a front and back porch, allowing your tenants to bask in the beauty of Duluth's stunning landscapes! As you step inside, you'll instantly be greeted by the warmth of natural woodwork, adding a touch of timeless elegance to each unit.   Two units are already occupied, meaning you won't have to waste time finding tenants. Units one and three are cozy spaces that feature one bedroom and a full bath, ensuring your tenants have all the comfort they need. The second unit offers even more flexibility with two bedrooms and another full bath. You have the power to transform this space into a truly exceptional living area.  Whether you're an experienced investor looking to expand your portfolio or a first-time buyer dipping your toes into the world of real estate, this tri-plex is an absolute gem. With the potential for multiple rental incomes, you can maximize your return on investment and secure a profitable future.   Don't wait any longer to make your mark on Duluth's real estate scene. This tri-plex offers endless possibilities and boundless potential. So seize this opportunity today and be a part of the exciting rental market in East Hillside Duluth. Your investment journey starts here! Contact us now to schedule a viewing and explore the endless possibilities that await you.
